library(tidyverse)
theme_set(theme_bw())
library(boot)
library(broom)
library(dplyr)
dados = read_csv(here::here("../result.csv"))
Missing column names filled in: 'X1' [1]
 Column specification 
cols(
  X1 = col_double(),
  puro_spearman = col_double(),
  pvalue = col_double(),
  method = col_character()
)
dados[is.na(dados)] = 0
dados %>% ggplot( aes(x=method, y = puro_spearman, color=method)) + 
                      geom_jitter(width = 0.2, height =.005, alpha = 0.2)+
    geom_violin(alpha = 0.2)+
    stat_summary(fun=mean, color = "black", alpha = 0.5)+
    labs(
         x = "Mtodo", 
         y = "Corr",
         title = "Corr por Mtodo"
    )

unique(dados$method)
[1] "XRAI"                             "SmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency" "GradientSaliency"                 "SmoothGradCAM"                    "SmoothGradientSaliency"           "IntegratedGradientSaliency"       "Blur"                            
thetaXRAI <- function(d, i) {
    methodSum = d %>%
        slice(i) %>% 
        group_by(method) %>% 
        summarise(media = mean(puro_spearman))
    saliencyMedia = methodSum %>% filter(method == "XRAI") %>% pull(media)
    saliencyMedia
}
bootXRAI = boot(data = dados,
           statistic = thetaXRAI,
           R = 2000) %>%
    tidy(conf.level = .95,
         conf.int = TRUE)
bootXRAI$nome = "XRAI"


thetaSmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency <- function(d, i) {
    methodSum = d %>%
        slice(i) %>% 
        group_by(method) %>% 
        summarise(media = mean(puro_spearman))
    saliencyMedia = methodSum %>% filter(method == "SmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency") %>% pull(media)
    saliencyMedia
}
bootSmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency  = boot(data = dados,
           statistic = thetaSmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency,
           R = 4000) %>%
    tidy(conf.level = .95,
         conf.int = TRUE)
bootSmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency$nome = "SmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency"

thetGradientSaliency <- function(d, i) {
    methodSum = d %>%
        slice(i) %>% 
        group_by(method) %>% 
        summarise(media = mean(puro_spearman))
    saliencyMedia = methodSum %>% filter(method == "GradientSaliency") %>% pull(media)
    saliencyMedia
}
bootGradientSaliency  = boot(data = dados,
           statistic = thetGradientSaliency,
           R = 4000) %>%
    tidy(conf.level = .95,
         conf.method = "bca",
         conf.int = TRUE)
bootGradientSaliency$nome = "GradientSaliency"

medias <- rbind(bootBlur, bootIntegratedGradientSaliency, bootSmoothGradientSaliency, bootSmoothGradCAM, bootGradientSaliency, bootSmoothIntegratedGradientSaliency, bootXRAI)
medias %>% 
  ggplot(aes(
            ymin = conf.low,
            y = statistic,
            ymax = conf.high,
            x = nome,
            color = nome
        )) +
        geom_linerange(color = "black") +
        geom_point(size = 1) +
        scale_y_continuous(limits = c(-.3, .3)) +
        labs(x = "", y = "IC 95% Mdia de Correlaco")+
    coord_flip()

thetaSaliencyGrad <- function(d, i) {
    methodSum = d %>%
        slice(i) %>% 
        group_by(method) %>% 
        summarise(media = mean(corr))
    saliencyMedia = methodSum %>% filter(method == \GradientSaliency\) %>% pull(media)
    gradMedia = methodSum %>% filter(method == \SmoothGradCAM\) %>% pull(media)
    saliencyMedia - gradMedia
}


bootSaliencyGrad = boot(data = dados,
           statistic = thetaSaliencyGrad,
           R = 2000) %>%
    tidy(conf.level = .95,
         conf.method = \bca\,
         conf.int = TRUE)
bootSaliencyGrad$nome = \GradientSaliency - SmoothGradCAM\
